    <title>New release for Pachli: Pachli 2.12.0</title>
    <updated>2025-04-30T08:44:15-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>pachli/pachli-android</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;New features and other improvements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update colour scheme, adjusts contrast (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1452"&gt;1452&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Move tab-tap behaviour preference out of "Lab experiments" (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1477"&gt;1477&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve the display of admin notifications (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1475"&gt;1475&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable client-side encrypted cloud backups (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1457"&gt;1457&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lab support for exporting/importing preferences (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1451"&gt;1451&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show hashtag usage and account stats in search results (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1442"&gt;1442&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show hashtag statistics in the Followed Tags screen (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1433"&gt;1433&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sort followed hashtags by hashtag name (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1432"&gt;1432&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Significant bug fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show translated posts / media descriptions when viewing threads (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1504"&gt;1504&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't error on nullable &lt;code&gt;Report.actionTakenAt&lt;/code&gt; property (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1474"&gt;1474&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set initial reading position for non-cached timelines to the top (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1468"&gt;1468&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Allow filtering of mentions and severed relationships on older devices (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1454"&gt;1454&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevent crash, correctly pass report data to notifications (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1449"&gt;1449&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=im@austinhuang.me"&gt;Austin Huang&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Allow clicks anywhere on FollowedTag view (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1445"&gt;1445&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevent "Record not found" when opening as a different account (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1431"&gt;1431&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
